{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":765,"text":"So let me start by taking you back,"},{"time":4367,"text":"back into the mists of your memory"},{"time":6603,"text":"to perhaps the most anticipated year in your life,"},{"time":10116,"text":"but certainly the most anticipated year"},{"time":12752,"text":"in all human history:"},{"time":14730,"text":"the year 2000. Remember that?"},{"time":17668,"text":"Y2K, the dotcom bubble,"},{"time":21221,"text":"stressing about whose party you're going to go to"},{"time":23618,"text":"as the clock strikes midnight,"},{"time":25840,"text":"before the champagne goes flat,"},{"time":27882,"text":"and then there's that inchoate yearning"},{"time":31201,"text":"that was felt, I think, by many, that the millennium,"},{"time":34440,"text":"that the year 2000, should mean more,"},{"time":36956,"text":"more than just a two and some zeroes."}]},{"cues":[{"time":40175,"text":"Well, amazingly, for once, our world leaders"},{"time":43933,"text":"actually lived up to that millennium moment"},{"time":46555,"text":"and back in 2000 agreed to some"},{"time":48704,"text":"pretty extraordinary stuff:"},{"time":51111,"text":"visionary, measurable, long-term targets"},{"time":54557,"text":"called the Millennium Development Goals."}]},{"cues":[{"time":57290,"text":"Now, I'm sure you all keep a copy of the goals"},{"time":59535,"text":"under your pillow, or by the bedside table,"},{"time":62317,"text":"but just in case you don't,"},{"time":64403,"text":"and your memory needs some jogging,"},{"time":66233,"text":"the deal agreed then goes like this:"},{"time":68855,"text":"developing countries promised to at least halve"},{"time":71430,"text":"extreme poverty, hunger and deaths from disease,"},{"time":74828,"text":"alongside some other targets, by 2015,"},{"time":77608,"text":"and developed nations promised to help them"},{"time":80463,"text":"get that done by dropping debts,"},{"time":82861,"text":"increasing smart aid, and trade reform."}]},{"cues":[{"time":85582,"text":"Well, we're approaching 2015,"},{"time":87831,"text":"so we'd better assess, how are we doing on these goals?"},{"time":90630,"text":"But we've also got to decide, do we like such global goals?"},{"time":94392,"text":"Some people don't. And if we like them, we've got to decide"},{"time":97631,"text":"what we want to do on these goals going forward."},{"time":100864,"text":"What does the world want to do together?"},{"time":103043,"text":"We've got to decide a process by which we decide."}]},{"cues":[{"time":105566,"text":"Well, I definitely think these goals are worth building on"},{"time":108464,"text":"and seeing through, and here's just a few reasons why."},{"time":112265,"text":"Incredible partnerships between the private sector,"},{"time":115382,"text":"political leaders, philanthropists"},{"time":117586,"text":"and amazing grassroots activists"},{"time":119615,"text":"across the developing world,"},{"time":121344,"text":"but also 250,000 people marched in the streets"},{"time":125878,"text":"of Edinburgh outside this very building"},{"time":128314,"text":"for Make Poverty History."}]},{"cues":[{"time":129658,"text":"All together, they achieved these results:"},{"time":132349,"text":"increased the number of people on anti-retrovirals,"},{"time":135441,"text":"life-saving anti-AIDS drugs;"},{"time":137614,"text":"nearly halved deaths from malaria;"},{"time":140302,"text":"vaccinated so many that 5.4 million lives will be saved."},{"time":145064,"text":"And combined, this is going to result"},{"time":147367,"text":"in two million fewer children dying every year,"},{"time":150450,"text":"last year, than in the year 2000."},{"time":152495,"text":"That's 5,000 fewer kids dying every day,"},{"time":155430,"text":"ten times you lot not dead every day,"},{"time":158974,"text":"because of all of these partnerships."},{"time":160956,"text":"So I think this is amazing living proof of progress"},{"time":164059,"text":"that more people should know about,"},{"time":166016,"text":"but the challenge of communicating this kind of good news"},{"time":168423,"text":"is probably the subject of a different TEDTalk."},{"time":171463,"text":"Anyway, for now, anyone involved in getting these results,"},{"time":173981,"text":"thank you. I think this proved these goals are worth it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":177192,"text":"But there's still a lot of unfinished business."},{"time":179809,"text":"Still, 7.6 million children die every year of preventable,"},{"time":184411,"text":"treatable diseases,"},{"time":186482,"text":"and 178 million kids are malnourished"},{"time":189215,"text":"to the point of stunting, a horrible term"},{"time":190645,"text":"which means physical and cognitive lifelong impairment."},{"time":194423,"text":"So there's plainly a lot more to do on the goals we've got."}]},{"cues":[{"time":196911,"text":"But then, a lot of people think there are things"},{"time":199959,"text":"that should have been in the original package"},{"time":201872,"text":"that weren't agreed back then that should now be included,"},{"time":204144,"text":"like sustainable development targets,"},{"time":206674,"text":"natural resource governance targets,"},{"time":208936,"text":"access to opportunity, to knowledge,"},{"time":211131,"text":"equity, fighting corruption."},{"time":213121,"text":"All of this is measurable and could be in the new goals."}]},{"cues":[{"time":215777,"text":"But the key thing here is,"},{"time":217745,"text":"what do you think should be in the new goals?"},{"time":219860,"text":"What do you want?"},{"time":221772,"text":"Are you annoyed that I didn't talk about gender equality"},{"time":224216,"text":"or education?"},{"time":226093,"text":"Should those be in the new package of goals?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":228479,"text":"And quite frankly, that's a good question,"},{"time":230493,"text":"but there's going to be some tough tradeoffs"},{"time":232439,"text":"and choices here, so you want to hope"},{"time":234395,"text":"that the process by which the world decides"},{"time":236332,"text":"these new goals is going to be legitimate, right?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":239571,"text":"Well, as we gather here in Edinburgh,"},{"time":241597,"text":"technocrats appointed by the U.N. and certain governments,"},{"time":244579,"text":"with the best intentions, are busying themselves"},{"time":247042,"text":"designing a new package of goals,"},{"time":249441,"text":"and currently they're doing that through pretty much the same old"},{"time":252761,"text":"late-20th-century, top-down, elite, closed process."}]},{"cues":[{"time":256494,"text":"But, of course, since then, the Web and mobile telephony,"},{"time":260296,"text":"along with ubiquitous reality TV formats"},{"time":263038,"text":"have spread all around the world."},{"time":265155,"text":"So what we'd like to propose is that we use them"},{"time":267939,"text":"to involve people from all around the world"},{"time":270961,"text":"in an historic first: the world's first truly global"},{"time":274730,"text":"poll and consultation, where everyone everywhere"},{"time":278320,"text":"has an equal voice for the very first time."}]},{"cues":[{"time":281668,"text":"I mean, wouldn't it be a huge historic missed opportunity"},{"time":285203,"text":"not to do this, given that we can?"},{"time":287851,"text":"There's hundreds of billions of your aid dollars at stake,"},{"time":292750,"text":"tens of millions of lives, or deaths, at stake,"},{"time":296696,"text":"and, I'd argue, the security and future"},{"time":299043,"text":"of you and your family is also at stake."}]},{"cues":[{"time":301506,"text":"So, if you're with me, I'd say there's three essential steps"},{"time":305095,"text":"in this crowdsourcing campaign:"},{"time":307450,"text":"collecting, connecting and committing."}]},{"cues":[{"time":310327,"text":"So first of all, we've got to ground this campaign"},{"time":312499,"text":"in core polling data."},{"time":314623,"text":"Let's go into every country that will let us in,"},{"time":316737,"text":"ask 1,001 people what they want"},{"time":319325,"text":"the new goals to be, making special efforts"},{"time":321385,"text":"to reach the poorest, those without access"},{"time":323624,"text":"to modern technology, and let's make sure that their views"},{"time":326673,"text":"are at the center of the goals going forward."}]},{"cues":[{"time":328957,"text":"Then, we've got to commission a baseline survey"},{"time":333052,"text":"to make sure we can monitor and progress the goals"},{"time":335292,"text":"going forward. The original goals didn't really have"},{"time":337318,"text":"good baseline survey data,"},{"time":339192,"text":"and we're going to need the help of big data through all of this process to make sure"},{"time":343584,"text":"we can really monitor the progress."}]},{"cues":[{"time":345656,"text":"And then we've got to connect with the big crowd."},{"time":348361,"text":"Now here, we see the role for an unprecedented coalition"},{"time":351478,"text":"of social media giants and upstarts,"},{"time":354448,"text":"telecoms companies, reality TV show formats,"},{"time":358397,"text":"gaming companies, telecoms, all of them together"},{"time":361895,"text":"in kind of their \"We Are The World\" moment."},{"time":365336,"text":"Could they come together and help"},{"time":367643,"text":"the Millennium Development Goals get rebranded"},{"time":370424,"text":"into the Millennial Generation's Goals?"},{"time":373448,"text":"And if just five percent of the five billion plus"},{"time":376261,"text":"who are currently connected made a comment,"},{"time":379508,"text":"and that comment turned into a commitment,"},{"time":381830,"text":"we could crowdsource a force of 300 million people"},{"time":384966,"text":"around the world to help see these goals through."}]},{"cues":[{"time":388384,"text":"If we have this collected data, and this connected crowd,"},{"time":391886,"text":"based upon our experience of campaigning"},{"time":393615,"text":"and getting world leaders to commit,"},{"time":395256,"text":"I think world leaders will commit"},{"time":396697,"text":"to most of the crowdsourced recommendations."}]},{"cues":[{"time":399104,"text":"But the question really is, through this process"},{"time":401727,"text":"will we all have become committed?"},{"time":404415,"text":"And if we are, are we ready to iterate, monitor"},{"time":407316,"text":"and provide feedback, make sure these promises"},{"time":409580,"text":"are really delivering results?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":411563,"text":"Well, there's some fantastic examples here to scale up,"},{"time":414764,"text":"mostly piloted within Africa, actually."},{"time":417476,"text":"There's Open Data Kenya, which geocodes"},{"time":419715,"text":"and crowdsources information about where projects are,"},{"time":422167,"text":"are they delivering results."},{"time":423754,"text":"Often, they're not in the right place."},{"time":425530,"text":"And Ushahidi, which means \"witness\" in Swahili,"},{"time":428984,"text":"which geocodes and crowdsources information"},{"time":431382,"text":"in complex emergencies to help target responses."},{"time":435295,"text":"This is some of the most exciting stuff"},{"time":438704,"text":"in development and democracy,"},{"time":440563,"text":"where citizens on the edge of a network"},{"time":442662,"text":"are helping to force open the process"},{"time":444603,"text":"to make sure that the big global aid promises"},{"time":447314,"text":"and vague stuff up at the top really delivers for people"},{"time":450768,"text":"at a grassroots level and inverts that pyramid."},{"time":454924,"text":"This openness, this forcing openness, is key,"},{"time":458436,"text":"and if it wasn't entirely transparent already,"},{"time":461372,"text":"I should be open: I've got a completely transparent agenda."}]},{"cues":[{"time":466016,"text":"Long-term trends suggest that this century"},{"time":468423,"text":"is going to be a tough place to live,"},{"time":470679,"text":"with population increases, consumption patterns increasing,"},{"time":474576,"text":"and conflict over scarce natural resources."},{"time":478010,"text":"And look at the state of global politics today."},{"time":481654,"text":"Look at the Rio Earth Summit that happened just last week,"},{"time":484755,"text":"or the Mexican G20, also last week."},{"time":487109,"text":"Both, if we're honest, a bust."},{"time":490020,"text":"Our world leaders, our global politics,"},{"time":492183,"text":"currently can't get it done."},{"time":494872,"text":"They need our help. They need the cavalry,"},{"time":498245,"text":"and the cavalry's not going to come from Mars."},{"time":500478,"text":"It's got to come from us, and I see this process"},{"time":503713,"text":"of deciding democratically in a bottom-up fashion"},{"time":506664,"text":"what the world wants to work on together"},{"time":509058,"text":"as one vital means by which we can crowdsource"},{"time":512425,"text":"the force to really build that constituency"},{"time":515753,"text":"that's going to reinvigorate global governance"},{"time":518184,"text":"in the 21st century."}]},{"cues":[{"time":520175,"text":"I started in 2000. Let me finish in 2030."}]},{"cues":[{"time":525304,"text":"Many people made fun of a big campaign a few years ago"},{"time":528803,"text":"we had called Make Poverty History."},{"time":530946,"text":"It was a naive thought in many people's minds,"},{"time":534236,"text":"and it's true, it was just a t-shirt slogan"},{"time":537005,"text":"that worked for the moment. But look."},{"time":540235,"text":"The empirical condition of living under a dollar and 25"},{"time":544380,"text":"is trending down, and look where it gets to by 2030."},{"time":547524,"text":"It's getting near zero."},{"time":549851,"text":"Now sure, progress in China and India"},{"time":552091,"text":"and poverty reduction there was key to that,"},{"time":554313,"text":"but recently also in Africa, poverty rates are being reduced."},{"time":557446,"text":"It will get harder as we get towards zero,"},{"time":560280,"text":"as the poor will be increasingly located"},{"time":562418,"text":"in post-conflict, fragile states,"},{"time":564708,"text":"or maybe in middle income states"},{"time":566684,"text":"where they don't really care about the marginalized."},{"time":569338,"text":"But I'm confident, with the right kind of political campaigning"},{"time":573285,"text":"and creative and technological innovation combined"},{"time":576447,"text":"working together more and more as one,"},{"time":578866,"text":"I think we can get this and other goals done."}]},{"cues":[{"time":582489,"text":"Thank you. (Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":585175,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":590500,"text":"Chris Anderson: Jamie, here's the puzzle to me."},{"time":592660,"text":"If there was an incident today where a hundred kids"},{"time":596436,"text":"died in some tragedy or where, say, a hundred kids"},{"time":599961,"text":"were kidnapped and then rescued by special forces,"},{"time":602852,"text":"I mean, it would be all over the news for a week, right?"},{"time":606106,"text":"You just put up, just as one of your numbers there,"},{"time":608726,"text":"that 5,000 -- is that the number?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":611808,"text":"Jamie Drummond: Fewer children every day."}]},{"cues":[{"time":613800,"text":"CA: Five thousand fewer children dying every day."},{"time":615471,"text":"I mean, it dwarfs, dwarfs everything"},{"time":618784,"text":"that is actually on our news agenda, and it's invisible."},{"time":622136,"text":"This must drive you crazy."}]},{"cues":[{"time":623970,"text":"JD: It does, and we're having a huge debate in this country"},{"time":626809,"text":"about aid levels, for example, and aid alone is not"},{"time":629324,"text":"the whole solution. Nobody thinks it is."},{"time":631642,"text":"But, you know, if people saw the results of this smart aid,"},{"time":636196,"text":"I mean, they'd be going crazy for it."},{"time":638665,"text":"I wish the 250,000 people who really did march"},{"time":642296,"text":"outside this very building knew these results."},{"time":645550,"text":"Right now they don't, and it would be great to find a way"},{"time":648429,"text":"to better communicate it, because we have not."},{"time":650681,"text":"Creatively, we've failed to communicate this success so far."},{"time":653963,"text":"If those kinds of efforts just could multiply their voice"},{"time":657171,"text":"and amplify it at the key moments, I know for a fact"},{"time":659680,"text":"we'd get better policy."},{"time":661681,"text":"The Mexican G20 need not have been a bust."},{"time":664202,"text":"Rio, if anyone cares about the environment,"},{"time":666743,"text":"need not have been a bust, okay?"},{"time":669085,"text":"But these conferences are going on,"},{"time":670955,"text":"and I know people get skeptical and cynical"},{"time":672652,"text":"about the big global summits and the promises"},{"time":674428,"text":"and their never being kept, but actually,"},{"time":676175,"text":"the bits that are, are making a difference,"},{"time":678558,"text":"and what the politicians need"},{"time":680007,"text":"is more permission from the public."}]},{"cues":[{"time":682248,"text":"CA: But you haven't fully worked out the Web mechanisms, etc."},{"time":684337,"text":"by which this might happen."},{"time":686297,"text":"I mean, if the people here who've had experience"},{"time":688184,"text":"using open platforms, you're interested to talk with them"},{"time":691344,"text":"this week and try to take this forward."}]},{"cues":[{"time":692970,"text":"JD: Absolutely. CA: All right, well I must say,"},{"time":694940,"text":"if this conference led in some way"},{"time":697552,"text":"to advancing that idea, that's a huge idea,"},{"time":700561,"text":"and if you carry that forward, that is really awesome,"},{"time":702918,"text":"so thank you. JD: I'd love your help."}]},{"cues":[{"time":704359,"text":"CA: Thank you, thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":706307,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}